WEBVTT

STYLE
::cue {
font-size: 1em;
font-weight: bold;
color: #ffffff;
}

00:01:31.180 --> 00:01:34.700 line:80%
=Generation to Generation=

00:01:34.820 --> 00:01:37.740 line:80%
=Episode 36=

00:01:46.180 --> 00:01:47.020 line:80%
Lingbo.

00:01:50.290 --> 00:01:51.196 line:80%
She's still breathing.

00:01:57.010 --> 00:01:57.850 line:80%
Mu Qingyan.

00:02:02.180 --> 00:02:04.820 line:80%
You found this place so soon.

00:02:05.850 --> 00:02:07.780 line:80%
Yuzhi told you, didn't he?

00:02:16.180 --> 00:02:17.180 line:80%
Since you're here,

00:02:17.860 --> 00:02:19.020 line:80%
neither of you can leave.

00:02:19.690 --> 00:02:21.180 line:80%
So, the man in black really is you.

00:02:21.860 --> 00:02:22.970 line:80%
I've always had a question.

00:02:23.620 --> 00:02:25.300 line:80%
You hate the Yins so much.

00:02:26.210 --> 00:02:27.620 line:80%
Why keep Song Yuzhi?

00:02:28.690 --> 00:02:30.060 line:80%
Isn't he Yin Dai's grandson?

00:02:30.490 --> 00:02:31.370 line:80%
He is different.

00:02:33.140 --> 00:02:35.340 line:80%
He grew up by my side,

00:02:35.340 --> 00:02:36.810 line:80%
personally taught by me.

00:02:36.810 --> 00:02:38.090 line:80%
He is not only gifted

00:02:38.090 --> 00:02:39.580 line:80%
but also refined and outstanding.

00:02:39.580 --> 00:02:41.090 line:80%
And he acts with composure,

00:02:41.810 --> 00:02:43.460 line:80%
upright and honorable.

00:02:44.180 --> 00:02:45.300 line:80%
He's the most suitable match

00:02:45.860 --> 00:02:47.620 line:80%
for Zhao.

00:02:47.620 --> 00:02:49.090 line:80%
Stop putting on this act.

00:02:50.460 --> 00:02:51.690 line:80%
Everything you've done

00:02:52.620 --> 00:02:55.020 line:80%
was to find the Jade Sunflower
for cultivation.

00:02:55.860 --> 00:02:57.673 line:80%
After returning empty-handed
from Chang Fort,

00:02:58.620 --> 00:03:00.690 line:80%
you lured Wu Gang to cultivate
the Nether Aura,

00:03:01.300 --> 00:03:02.620 line:80%
causing Song Yuzhi to be poisoned.

00:03:03.580 --> 00:03:04.740 line:80%
Because you knew

00:03:04.740 --> 00:03:06.410 line:80%
Zhao and Song Yuzhi were close.

00:03:06.410 --> 00:03:08.180 line:80%
She'd never stand by and do nothing.

00:03:08.180 --> 00:03:09.860 line:80%
The final clue to the Jade Sunflower

00:03:09.860 --> 00:03:10.810 line:80%
was in Luoying Valley.

00:03:11.740 --> 00:03:13.020 line:80%
Only by doing this

00:03:13.020 --> 00:03:15.740 line:80%
might the Jade Sunflower,
missing for over a decade,

00:03:15.740 --> 00:03:17.090 line:80%
reappear in the world.

00:03:18.900 --> 00:03:20.090 line:80%
Lord Qi,

00:03:20.090 --> 00:03:21.140 line:80%
you keep saying

00:03:21.140 --> 00:03:22.740 line:80%
it's for Song Yuzhi and Zhao's good.

00:03:23.490 --> 00:03:25.530 line:80%
But you've been using them all along.

00:03:25.530 --> 00:03:26.930 line:80%
There's no point talking to you.

00:03:27.340 --> 00:03:28.210 line:80%
Everything I've done

00:03:29.180 --> 00:03:31.090 line:80%
is for a great cause.

00:03:32.460 --> 00:03:33.530 line:80%
What great cause?

00:03:33.530 --> 00:03:34.740 line:80%
What revenge?

00:03:34.740 --> 00:03:36.180 line:80%
What reshaping Jianghu?

00:03:36.180 --> 00:03:37.650 line:80%
In the end,

00:03:37.650 --> 00:03:39.580 line:80%
it's just sacrificing others' lives

00:03:39.580 --> 00:03:40.620 line:80%
for your selfish desires.

00:03:41.300 --> 00:03:42.340 line:80%
How are you

00:03:42.780 --> 00:03:44.530 line:80%
any different from Yin Dai?

00:03:44.530 --> 00:03:45.900 line:80%
So what?

00:03:58.900 --> 00:04:00.340 line:80%
The Sevens Poison.

00:04:00.340 --> 00:04:01.650 line:80%
When did you poison him?

00:04:01.650 --> 00:04:02.650 line:80%
Back at Xuankong Nunnery.

00:04:10.970 --> 00:04:11.810 line:80%
Watch out!

00:04:16.380 --> 00:04:18.060 line:80%
Why does the poison
have no effect on you?

00:04:18.580 --> 00:04:20.530 line:80%
I have the Tianhuo Dragon Bone.

00:04:21.380 --> 00:04:22.766 line:80%
All poisons are useless against me.

00:04:24.090 --> 00:04:26.610 line:80%
You two can't stop me.

00:04:26.610 --> 00:04:28.340 line:80%
Since you are immune to poison,

00:04:28.340 --> 00:04:29.730 line:80%
why could Wu Gang

00:04:29.730 --> 00:04:31.380 line:80%
switch you?

00:04:35.090 --> 00:04:36.460 line:80%
You were never poisoned.

00:04:37.050 --> 00:04:38.460 line:80%
From beginning to end,

00:04:38.460 --> 00:04:39.500 line:80%
you were just pretending.

00:04:40.090 --> 00:04:41.380 line:80%
You allowed Wu Gang and Wu Xiong

00:04:41.380 --> 00:04:42.650 line:80%
to go to the sect.

00:04:42.650 --> 00:04:43.970 line:80%
Did you also arrange

00:04:43.970 --> 00:04:45.530 line:80%
Ms. Luo's appearance

00:04:45.530 --> 00:04:46.700 line:80%
at the memorial?

00:04:47.500 --> 00:04:48.340 line:80%
That's right.

00:04:49.380 --> 00:04:51.140 line:80%
I wanted to use Luo Yuanrong

00:04:52.170 --> 00:04:53.970 line:80%
to tear apart Yin Dai's false mask.

00:04:54.820 --> 00:04:56.650 line:80%
But I never expected

00:04:56.650 --> 00:04:59.580 line:80%
Nie Zhe to fish in troubled waters,

00:04:59.580 --> 00:05:01.530 line:80%
using Qianmian Sect to stir up trouble.

00:05:01.530 --> 00:05:03.050 line:80%
So, I went along with the plan.

00:05:03.850 --> 00:05:04.940 line:80%
Just in time

00:05:04.940 --> 00:05:06.970 line:80%
to dampen the spirit of the Six Sects.

00:05:06.970 --> 00:05:08.610 line:80%
So, you kept pretending

00:05:09.410 --> 00:05:11.020 line:80%
until I helped you retrieve the saliva.

00:05:11.700 --> 00:05:12.540 line:80%
Zhao,

00:05:13.210 --> 00:05:14.820 line:80%
I didn't want you to take risks.

00:05:15.780 --> 00:05:16.900 line:80%
But I had no choice.

00:05:17.380 --> 00:05:18.530 line:80%
In this world,

00:05:18.530 --> 00:05:19.970 line:80%
only the Cais

00:05:19.970 --> 00:05:21.850 line:80%
can find the saliva.

00:05:21.850 --> 00:05:23.530 line:80%
Only after obtaining it

00:05:23.530 --> 00:05:25.850 line:80%
can I cultivate the Ziwei Method

00:05:25.850 --> 00:05:27.170 line:80%
and avenge your aunt.

00:05:27.970 --> 00:05:30.340 line:80%
No wonder the Body Shift was so strange.

00:05:31.340 --> 00:05:32.850 line:80%
But after all your calculations,

00:05:32.850 --> 00:05:35.380 line:80%
you didn't expect Zhao to go
to Li Sect to help me

00:05:35.380 --> 00:05:37.170 line:80%
and to learn about the man in black.

00:05:37.650 --> 00:05:40.020 line:80%
If Zhao and Yuzhi
hadn't been there that day,

00:05:40.020 --> 00:05:41.140 line:80%
I would've killed you.

00:05:42.700 --> 00:05:44.900 line:80%
If I'd killed you then,

00:05:44.900 --> 00:05:46.500 line:80%
nothing would've happened.

00:05:46.500 --> 00:05:47.660 line:80%
Though you failed to kill me,

00:05:48.650 --> 00:05:50.090 line:80%
you killed Sun Ruoshui to silence her

00:05:50.820 --> 00:05:51.940 line:80%
and rescued Nie Zhe.

00:05:52.580 --> 00:05:54.050 line:80%
The ambush at the Chang graveyard

00:05:54.940 --> 00:05:56.610 line:80%
and the attack by the riverside

00:05:57.460 --> 00:05:59.210 line:80%
were done by your men.

00:05:59.210 --> 00:06:00.610 line:80%
No wonder those assassins

00:06:00.610 --> 00:06:01.700 line:80%
kept showing mercy to Zhao,

00:06:02.970 --> 00:06:04.380 line:80%
yet struck at me with killing blows.

00:06:05.730 --> 00:06:07.456 line:80%
Unfortunately,
Zhao was soft-hearted then

00:06:07.467 --> 00:06:09.367 line:80%
and refused to believe
it was done by her sect.

00:06:10.090 --> 00:06:11.340 line:80%
Later on,

00:06:11.340 --> 00:06:13.610 line:80%
you used Song Xiuzhi
to throw Guangtian Sect into chaos.

00:06:13.610 --> 00:06:15.900 line:80%
Not only to weaken their strength,

00:06:15.900 --> 00:06:17.540 line:80%
but also to lure Zhao

00:06:17.551 --> 00:06:18.953 line:80%
into going to the Blood Marsh Forest

00:06:19.500 --> 00:06:20.610 line:80%
to find the Night Orchid.

00:06:21.090 --> 00:06:23.742 line:80%
You also ordered Song Xiuzhi to use

00:06:23.753 --> 00:06:25.020 line:80%
the poisoned dart on Song Yuzhi.

00:06:25.020 --> 00:06:27.050 line:80%
I told Song Xiuzhi

00:06:27.050 --> 00:06:28.820 line:80%
not to harm Yuzhi's life.

00:06:29.380 --> 00:06:31.340 line:80%
You still don't understand humans.

00:06:32.050 --> 00:06:33.700 line:80%
Song Xiuzhi is narrow-minded.

00:06:34.340 --> 00:06:35.306 line:80%
How could he show mercy?

00:06:36.380 --> 00:06:38.140 line:80%
If Zhao hadn't risked her life
to save him,

00:06:38.780 --> 00:06:40.700 line:80%
Song Yuzhi would already be dead.

00:06:42.380 --> 00:06:43.900 line:80%
Mr. Chang once said

00:06:43.900 --> 00:06:45.700 line:80%
that selfish desires

00:06:45.700 --> 00:06:47.900 line:80%
lead to countless mistakes.

00:06:47.900 --> 00:06:49.410 line:80%
In fact,

00:06:49.410 --> 00:06:50.780 line:80%
before Mr. Chang died,

00:06:50.780 --> 00:06:52.940 line:80%
he already suspected Qingque Sect.

00:06:52.940 --> 00:06:54.820 line:80%
And he vaguely sensed

00:06:54.820 --> 00:06:56.730 line:80%
who the mastermind

00:06:56.730 --> 00:06:58.140 line:80%
behind everything was.

00:06:58.140 --> 00:06:59.660 line:80%
The one who leaked the Six Sects' info

00:06:59.671 --> 00:07:00.994 line:80%
and exposed Yin Dai's whereabouts

00:07:01.005 --> 00:07:02.562 line:80%
(Chang Fort)
should be the same person.

00:07:02.573 --> 00:07:03.610 line:80%
After Pingshu died,

00:07:05.210 --> 00:07:06.650 line:80%
Nie Zhe began making moves again.

00:07:06.650 --> 00:07:09.140 line:80%
There seemed to be an insider.

00:07:09.900 --> 00:07:11.340 line:80%
I secretly investigated one by one.

00:07:11.340 --> 00:07:12.900 line:80%
Only one person was the most suspicious.

00:07:12.900 --> 00:07:15.170 line:80%
He had deep ties to Qingque Sect.

00:07:15.170 --> 00:07:16.090 line:80%
But

00:07:17.090 --> 00:07:18.820 line:80%
since Uncle Chang suspected Master,

00:07:19.380 --> 00:07:20.700 line:80%
why did he entrust you to Master

00:07:21.290 --> 00:07:22.650 line:80%
before he died?

00:07:22.650 --> 00:07:23.850 line:80%
The most dangerous place

00:07:24.730 --> 00:07:26.170 line:80%
is the safest place.

00:07:28.050 --> 00:07:29.650 line:80%
Mr. Mu,

00:07:29.650 --> 00:07:31.610 line:80%
I can no longer protect you.

00:07:31.610 --> 00:07:33.900 line:80%
The only place that can keep you safe

00:07:33.900 --> 00:07:35.050 line:80%
is Qingque Sect.

00:07:35.770 --> 00:07:36.610 line:80%
Remember:

00:07:36.610 --> 00:07:39.380 line:80%
You're my son Chang Ning.

00:07:46.900 --> 00:07:47.940 line:80%
Mr. Chang

00:07:47.940 --> 00:07:49.020 line:80%
realized Lord Qi

00:07:49.020 --> 00:07:51.380 line:80%
had noticed the secret investigation.

00:07:51.380 --> 00:07:52.900 line:80%
So, before his death,

00:07:52.900 --> 00:07:54.566 line:80%
without showing
the slightest hesitation,

00:07:54.577 --> 00:07:56.290 line:80%
he entrusted his only son
to Qingque Sect.

00:07:56.290 --> 00:07:58.410 line:80%
Only then could he dispel
Lord Qi's suspicions.

00:07:59.050 --> 00:08:01.170 line:80%
I underestimated Chang.

00:08:03.610 --> 00:08:04.500 line:80%
Master.

00:08:06.580 --> 00:08:07.420 line:80%
Zhao.

00:08:08.650 --> 00:08:09.500 line:80%
I know

00:08:09.500 --> 00:08:11.380 line:80%
everything you've done was for Aunt.

00:08:13.410 --> 00:08:14.820 line:80%
It's enough already.

00:08:14.820 --> 00:08:15.780 line:80%
Stop.

00:08:16.650 --> 00:08:17.490 line:80%
No.

00:08:18.020 --> 00:08:20.170 line:80%
My cultivation is about to succeed.

00:08:20.610 --> 00:08:22.500 line:80%
Then, I'll be invincible in the world,

00:08:23.340 --> 00:08:24.610 line:80%
with no one to fear.

00:08:25.210 --> 00:08:26.090 line:80%
I'll hold

00:08:26.090 --> 00:08:27.090 line:80%
a grand wedding

00:08:28.290 --> 00:08:30.530 line:80%
for you and Yuzhi.

00:08:30.530 --> 00:08:31.370 line:80%
All right?

00:08:47.690 --> 00:08:49.740 line:80%
Oh, no. He's reaching the final level.

00:08:50.740 --> 00:08:51.580 line:80%
Master.

00:08:51.810 --> 00:08:52.900 line:80%
Master!

00:08:52.900 --> 00:08:54.450 line:80%
She's your daughter!

00:10:30.740 --> 00:10:31.980 line:80%
This is Qingque Sect.

00:10:32.810 --> 00:10:33.740 line:80%
What are you doing?

00:10:34.220 --> 00:10:35.140 line:80%
Rebelling?

00:10:35.140 --> 00:10:36.020 line:80%
Yang Heying!

00:10:50.500 --> 00:10:51.740 line:80%
What are you doing here?

00:10:52.140 --> 00:10:53.620 line:80%
Naturally, to settle grievances

00:10:54.100 --> 00:10:55.170 line:80%
and take revenge.

00:10:57.530 --> 00:10:59.140 line:80%
Lord Cai, Lady Ning,

00:10:59.140 --> 00:11:00.780 line:80%
go find Zhao first.

00:11:00.780 --> 00:11:01.810 line:80%
After I finish my father,

00:11:01.810 --> 00:11:03.020 line:80%
I'll go meet you.

00:11:04.290 --> 00:11:05.150 line:80%
Xiaolan,

00:11:05.220 --> 00:11:06.900 line:80%
let us deal with him for you.

00:11:07.500 --> 00:11:08.690 line:80%
Let me do it.

00:11:09.053 --> 00:11:10.853 line:80%
I want to avenge my mother
with my own hands.

00:11:11.290 --> 00:11:12.130 line:80%
Don't act recklessly.

00:11:13.140 --> 00:11:13.980 line:80%
Shangguan,

00:11:14.220 --> 00:11:15.500 line:80%
stay here and support Xiaolan.

00:11:16.100 --> 00:11:17.140 line:80%
Don't worry.

00:11:18.100 --> 00:11:19.450 line:80%
None of you will escape.

00:11:19.900 --> 00:11:20.740 line:80%
Attack!

00:11:39.290 --> 00:11:40.690 line:80%
You think you can take revenge?

00:11:51.500 --> 00:11:52.780 line:80%
Storm Axe Blade.

00:11:52.780 --> 00:11:54.530 line:80%
My grandfather's famous weapon.

00:11:55.570 --> 00:11:57.100 line:80%
After he was injured and retired,

00:11:57.100 --> 00:11:58.766 line:80%
he secretly had someone
deliver it to me.

00:11:59.500 --> 00:12:01.140 line:80%
He told me to train diligently.

00:12:01.140 --> 00:12:02.342 line:80%
He said that even as a woman,

00:12:02.353 --> 00:12:04.140 line:80%
one should have a world of her own,

00:12:04.140 --> 00:12:05.740 line:80%
just like Ms. Cai.

00:12:05.740 --> 00:12:06.860 line:80%
What nonsense.

00:12:06.860 --> 00:12:08.380 line:80%
Who'd draw a blade at their father?

00:12:09.050 --> 00:12:10.980 line:80%
You are worse than beasts.

00:12:10.980 --> 00:12:13.290 line:80%
You brought it upon yourself.

00:12:19.650 --> 00:12:20.780 line:80%
Yang Heying,

00:12:20.780 --> 00:12:21.690 line:80%
please.

00:12:27.220 --> 00:12:28.060 line:80%
Yuzhi.

00:12:28.650 --> 00:12:29.860 line:80%
The grudges between us

00:12:31.140 --> 00:12:32.980 line:80%
should be settled by ourselves.

00:12:33.530 --> 00:12:34.780 line:80%
Father is still alive.

00:12:35.170 --> 00:12:36.980 line:80%
He's still the Lord of Guangtian Sect.

00:12:36.980 --> 00:12:38.810 line:80%
Are you planning to defy him?

00:12:38.810 --> 00:12:39.650 line:80%
Ridiculous.

00:12:39.650 --> 00:12:41.230 line:80%
You betrayed your master and ancestors.

00:12:41.241 --> 00:12:42.647 line:80%
You are no longer part of our sect.

00:12:43.220 --> 00:12:44.410 line:80%
The Lord's token is here.

00:12:44.780 --> 00:12:46.410 line:80%
It represents the Lord.

00:12:46.633 --> 00:12:48.352 line:80%
The Lord is recuperating
in Luoying Valley.

00:12:48.363 --> 00:12:49.483 line:80%
He will soon recover.

00:12:50.050 --> 00:12:52.020 line:80%
Then, he'll surely settle accounts
with you,

00:12:52.020 --> 00:12:54.020 line:80%
the traitor who harmed his family.

00:12:54.020 --> 00:12:54.860 line:80%
Shut up!

00:12:55.410 --> 00:12:56.780 line:80%
I've defeated Song Yuzhi.

00:12:57.220 --> 00:12:58.620 line:80%
I am the new Lord.

00:12:58.620 --> 00:13:00.220 line:80%
Last time, my injuries had not healed.

00:13:00.220 --> 00:13:01.100 line:80%
Xiuzhi,

00:13:01.100 --> 00:13:02.780 line:80%
do you dare compete again?

00:13:03.650 --> 00:13:04.650 line:80%
Bring it on.

00:14:17.140 --> 00:14:18.220 line:80%
You really want to kill me?

00:14:18.690 --> 00:14:19.530 line:80%
Don't worry.

00:14:20.410 --> 00:14:21.650 line:80%
After you die,

00:14:21.650 --> 00:14:23.380 line:80%
I'll raise my little brother.

00:14:24.500 --> 00:14:25.620 line:80%
He was born weak.

00:14:25.620 --> 00:14:27.650 line:80%
He can't cultivate
advanced martial arts anyway.

00:14:27.650 --> 00:14:29.930 line:80%
I'll have someone teach him
reading and writing.

00:14:29.930 --> 00:14:31.500 line:80%
He can live as a humble farmer.

00:14:33.140 --> 00:14:35.450 line:80%
As for the lord position of Siqi Sect,

00:14:35.930 --> 00:14:37.100 line:80%
I'll take it.

00:14:38.650 --> 00:14:40.780 line:80%
Surely, many elders will oppose it.

00:14:40.780 --> 00:14:42.220 line:80%
But that doesn't matter.

00:14:42.220 --> 00:14:44.500 line:80%
I'll make them submit one by one.

00:14:44.500 --> 00:14:46.269 line:80%
All these years,
when you committed crimes,

00:14:46.280 --> 00:14:47.930 line:80%
they said nothing.

00:14:47.930 --> 00:14:49.810 line:80%
So, when I become the Lord,

00:14:49.810 --> 00:14:52.100 line:80%
why should they jump out
with righteous speeches?

00:14:52.780 --> 00:14:53.620 line:80%
Father,

00:14:54.450 --> 00:14:55.290 line:80%
don't you think so?

00:14:56.130 --> 00:14:56.980 line:80%
Xiaolan,

00:14:56.980 --> 00:14:58.220 line:80%
I am your father.

00:14:58.220 --> 00:15:00.170 line:80%
Your father bound to you by blood.

00:15:01.980 --> 00:15:02.980 line:80%
I was wrong.

00:15:05.290 --> 00:15:06.130 line:80%
How about this?

00:15:06.290 --> 00:15:07.263 line:80%
Cripple my martial arts.

00:15:08.140 --> 00:15:09.500 line:80%
Imprison me.

00:15:09.500 --> 00:15:10.860 line:80%
Let me suffer.

00:15:10.860 --> 00:15:11.930 line:80%
Let me repent.

00:15:12.810 --> 00:15:13.690 line:80%
Let me feel regret.

00:15:33.020 --> 00:15:34.220 line:80%
You couldn't do it, so I did.

00:15:35.050 --> 00:15:36.783 line:80%
I don't want his blood
to stain your hands.

00:15:57.690 --> 00:15:58.780 line:80%
Grandfather.

00:16:00.100 --> 00:16:00.940 line:80%
Uncle.

00:16:01.500 --> 00:16:02.340 line:80%
Mother.

00:16:03.570 --> 00:16:04.570 line:80%
I have

00:16:04.980 --> 00:16:05.820 line:80%
avenged you.

00:16:07.220 --> 00:16:08.620 line:80%
May your spirits in heaven

00:16:10.020 --> 00:16:10.930 line:80%
rest in peace.

00:16:35.860 --> 00:16:36.700 line:80%
Li, Xuankong Nunnery

00:16:36.930 --> 00:16:38.500 line:80%
has long withdrawn from the world.

00:16:38.810 --> 00:16:40.330 line:80%
Why did you massacre everyone?

00:16:40.620 --> 00:16:41.740 line:80%
Because they did

00:16:42.100 --> 00:16:43.810 line:80%
the most hateful thing in this world.

00:16:44.290 --> 00:16:46.290 line:80%
Those hermits deserve death.

00:16:46.690 --> 00:16:48.220 line:80%
What kind of absurd logic is that?

00:16:48.220 --> 00:16:50.500 line:80%
Uncle Cheng and my master
died mysteriously.

00:16:50.860 --> 00:16:52.140 line:80%
But when they were buried,

00:16:53.423 --> 00:16:55.516 line:80%
those so-called righteous sects
didn't dare question

00:16:55.780 --> 00:16:57.980 line:80%
because Yin Dai was the Lord

00:16:58.780 --> 00:17:00.290 line:80%
of the foremost sect.

00:17:01.140 --> 00:17:02.020 line:80%
That day,

00:17:02.020 --> 00:17:04.740 line:80%
heroes gathered
atop the Thousandfold Cliff.

00:17:05.660 --> 00:17:07.500 line:80%
In the end, only Cai Pingshu

00:17:07.500 --> 00:17:08.700 line:80%
dared to speak up for justice.

00:17:09.130 --> 00:17:10.370 line:80%
The matter was strange.

00:17:10.660 --> 00:17:11.890 line:80%
Do you still remember?

00:17:11.890 --> 00:17:12.810 line:80%
Indeed.

00:17:14.050 --> 00:17:16.570 line:80%
Only Pingshu questioned it at that time.

00:17:16.980 --> 00:17:18.530 line:80%
Others also felt something was odd,

00:17:18.530 --> 00:17:19.890 line:80%
but out of courtesy,

00:17:19.890 --> 00:17:21.180 line:80%
they could not say much.

00:17:25.090 --> 00:17:27.220 line:80%
How laughable.

00:17:28.370 --> 00:17:30.020 line:80%
Thousands of heroes

00:17:30.780 --> 00:17:32.460 line:80%
were not as brave as a woman.

00:17:32.740 --> 00:17:34.270 line:80%
I know there is hatred in your heart.

00:17:34.560 --> 00:17:35.420 line:80%
But you can't...

00:17:35.420 --> 00:17:36.460 line:80%
What?

00:17:36.460 --> 00:17:37.766 line:80%
Now, I stand alone in this world.

00:17:38.500 --> 00:17:39.660 line:80%
I have nothing left to fear.

00:17:40.130 --> 00:17:41.940 line:80%
After my master and uncle's funeral,

00:17:42.460 --> 00:17:44.050 line:80%
Yin Dai used revenge as an excuse

00:17:44.050 --> 00:17:45.890 line:80%
to incite my fellow disciples

00:17:45.890 --> 00:17:47.810 line:80%
to fight the demonic sect to the death.

00:17:47.810 --> 00:17:49.330 line:80%
Even though they were outnumbered,

00:17:50.530 --> 00:17:52.700 line:80%
he still forced them to go die.

00:17:53.850 --> 00:17:54.690 line:80%
If they refused,

00:17:56.090 --> 00:17:57.610 line:80%
they were called ungrateful,

00:17:59.700 --> 00:18:01.530 line:80%
accused of betraying
their master's grace.

00:18:05.610 --> 00:18:06.810 line:80%
In just two short years,

00:18:07.460 --> 00:18:09.980 line:80%
I watched as my fellow disciples,

00:18:11.460 --> 00:18:12.530 line:80%
wave after wave,

00:18:13.460 --> 00:18:15.050 line:80%
went to their deaths.

00:18:16.660 --> 00:18:17.980 line:80%
No one spoke up for them.

00:18:20.330 --> 00:18:21.370 line:80%
In the end,

00:18:23.220 --> 00:18:24.610 line:80%
only I remained.

00:18:24.610 --> 00:18:25.740 line:80%
I know you are in pain.

00:18:27.810 --> 00:18:29.890 line:80%
But Yin Dai is the real culprit.

00:18:29.890 --> 00:18:31.780 line:80%
Why drag Chang into this?

00:18:32.530 --> 00:18:33.810 line:80%
Back at the funeral,

00:18:34.370 --> 00:18:35.610 line:80%
my father was not present.

00:18:36.020 --> 00:18:37.006 line:80%
He knew nothing about it.

00:18:37.330 --> 00:18:38.700 line:80%
What did he do wrong?

00:18:38.980 --> 00:18:40.290 line:80%
Why did you kill him?

00:18:40.740 --> 00:18:42.420 line:80%
That doesn't mean he was innocent.

00:18:42.890 --> 00:18:43.980 line:80%
Those who died...

00:18:44.290 --> 00:18:45.500 line:80%
Who among you remembers them?

00:18:46.180 --> 00:18:47.020 line:80%
Li,

00:18:47.570 --> 00:18:49.220 line:80%
since you remember Pingshu's kindness,

00:18:49.220 --> 00:18:51.290 line:80%
can't you, for her sake,

00:18:51.290 --> 00:18:52.420 line:80%
let this go?

00:18:52.890 --> 00:18:53.730 line:80%
Xiaofeng,

00:18:55.220 --> 00:18:56.660 line:80%
others may not know,

00:18:56.660 --> 00:18:58.370 line:80%
but you should understand.

00:18:58.370 --> 00:19:01.330 line:80%
Everything Yunke and I are doing now

00:19:01.330 --> 00:19:03.290 line:80%
is for Cai Pingshu.

00:19:03.290 --> 00:19:05.090 line:80%
The people you protect

00:19:05.090 --> 00:19:07.740 line:80%
watched as Cai Pingshu

00:19:07.740 --> 00:19:09.180 line:80%
went alone to Mount Tu

00:19:09.180 --> 00:19:10.940 line:80%
to kill Nie Hengcheng.

00:19:10.940 --> 00:19:13.180 line:80%
While she risked her life
fighting alone,

00:19:13.180 --> 00:19:14.740 line:80%
what were they doing?

00:19:14.740 --> 00:19:15.940 line:80%
One by one, they hid safely

00:19:15.940 --> 00:19:18.130 line:80%
in their own corners,

00:19:18.130 --> 00:19:20.780 line:80%
watching her risk her life for them.

00:19:20.780 --> 00:19:21.780 line:80%
Stop talking.

00:19:22.610 --> 00:19:24.330 line:80%
When my sister went alone to Mount Tu,

00:19:24.330 --> 00:19:25.780 line:80%
it was her own choice.

00:19:26.370 --> 00:19:27.890 line:80%
She never regretted it.

00:19:28.290 --> 00:19:29.130 line:80%
So,

00:19:30.460 --> 00:19:32.980 line:80%
no one needs to seek justice
on her behalf.

00:19:34.050 --> 00:19:36.090 line:80%
Today, I only have one thing to say.

00:19:36.090 --> 00:19:38.050 line:80%
Tell Qi Yunke to come out.

00:19:39.530 --> 00:19:41.130 line:80%
I'll speak to him face-to-face.

00:19:41.460 --> 00:19:42.660 line:80%
In that case,

00:19:44.130 --> 00:19:46.050 line:80%
let death decide the outcome.

00:20:22.130 --> 00:20:22.970 line:80%
Master.

00:20:23.890 --> 00:20:24.730 line:80%
Master,

00:20:24.850 --> 00:20:26.530 line:80%
they're breaking in. What to do?

00:20:26.530 --> 00:20:27.370 line:80%
Why panic?

00:20:27.660 --> 00:20:29.890 line:80%
Once I reach the final level,

00:20:29.890 --> 00:20:30.890 line:80%
those clowns outside

00:20:31.370 --> 00:20:32.420 line:80%
will be nothing to fear.

00:20:33.330 --> 00:20:34.170 line:80%
Master,

00:20:34.810 --> 00:20:35.980 line:80%
you don't look well.

00:20:36.700 --> 00:20:38.290 line:80%
Give me two Purging Pills.

00:20:46.700 --> 00:20:47.540 line:80%
Why?

00:20:48.020 --> 00:20:49.570 line:80%
I've always treated you well.

00:20:49.570 --> 00:20:51.330 line:80%
Pingshu even saved your life.

00:20:52.330 --> 00:20:53.700 line:80%
Why did you do this?

00:20:53.700 --> 00:20:55.130 line:80%
I can't watch you

00:20:55.130 --> 00:20:56.370 line:80%
commit another grave mistake.

00:20:56.980 --> 00:20:59.460 line:80%
You've already killed Lady Yin.

00:20:59.460 --> 00:21:00.810 line:80%
Spare Lingbo.

00:21:00.810 --> 00:21:02.050 line:80%
All for that woman?

00:21:02.660 --> 00:21:03.740 line:80%
That cold-blooded,

00:21:03.740 --> 00:21:04.580 line:80%
selfish,

00:21:04.940 --> 00:21:06.420 line:80%
hypocritical woman?

00:21:06.420 --> 00:21:08.290 line:80%
You'd betray Pingshu and me for her?

00:21:19.740 --> 00:21:20.580 line:80%
Master,

00:21:20.980 --> 00:21:22.090 line:80%
you and Ms. Cai

00:21:22.090 --> 00:21:23.740 line:80%
gave me a second life.

00:21:25.180 --> 00:21:26.660 line:80%
If you command it,

00:21:27.370 --> 00:21:28.890 line:80%
I'd give my life without hesitation.

00:21:29.570 --> 00:21:30.410 line:80%
However,

00:21:31.330 --> 00:21:33.220 line:80%
one's conscience

00:21:33.780 --> 00:21:36.500 line:80%
can never truly be extinguished.

00:21:39.180 --> 00:21:40.020 line:80%
Master,

00:21:40.330 --> 00:21:41.290 line:80%
Ms. Cai would never wish

00:21:41.780 --> 00:21:44.780 line:80%
to see you slay your kin for revenge.

00:21:46.890 --> 00:21:47.940 line:80%
Forgive me!

00:22:13.780 --> 00:22:14.940 line:80%
Dalou.

00:22:14.940 --> 00:22:16.370 line:80%
Take Lingbo and leave.

00:22:16.890 --> 00:22:17.730 line:80%
Hurry!

00:22:22.660 --> 00:22:23.500 line:80%
Dalou.

00:22:24.660 --> 00:22:25.890 line:80%
Go.

00:22:48.370 --> 00:22:50.020 line:80%
Go!

00:23:13.570 --> 00:23:15.180 line:80%
Veilbreaker.

00:23:16.530 --> 00:23:18.180 line:80%
You've mastered it.

00:23:23.700 --> 00:23:24.940 line:80%
Kill me.

00:23:39.850 --> 00:23:40.690 line:80%
Watch out!

00:24:09.540 --> 00:24:10.820 line:80%
(Righteous Spirit)

00:24:31.890 --> 00:24:32.740 line:80%
Zhao,

00:24:32.740 --> 00:24:33.940 line:80%
give Lingbo to me.

00:24:35.290 --> 00:24:36.890 line:80%
I'm almost there.

00:24:37.290 --> 00:24:38.130 line:80%
Master,

00:24:38.890 --> 00:24:40.090 line:80%
wake up.

00:24:40.090 --> 00:24:41.420 line:80%
You'll get her killed!

00:24:41.420 --> 00:24:42.810 line:80%
Give her to me.

00:24:47.890 --> 00:24:49.370 line:80%
Forgive me.

00:25:01.890 --> 00:25:03.500 line:80%
You're just like Mu Zhengyang.

00:25:04.050 --> 00:25:05.700 line:80%
A skin-painted demon.

00:25:06.420 --> 00:25:07.940 line:80%
Constantly bewitching Zhao.

00:25:08.420 --> 00:25:09.290 line:80%
Otherwise,

00:25:09.610 --> 00:25:11.050 line:80%
why would she get involved in this

00:25:11.530 --> 00:25:13.500 line:80%
and suffer the lashes?

00:25:19.810 --> 00:25:20.810 line:80%
Master,

00:25:21.940 --> 00:25:23.330 line:80%
he's never harmed me.

00:25:24.610 --> 00:25:26.220 line:80%
Please don't hurt him.

00:25:26.220 --> 00:25:27.660 line:80%
He almost got you killed!

00:25:28.020 --> 00:25:28.860 line:80%
If not for him,

00:25:29.220 --> 00:25:30.880 line:80%
I wouldn't have used
the Withered Branch.

00:25:31.113 --> 00:25:32.782 line:80%
Nor would there have been
all the trouble

00:25:32.793 --> 00:25:33.903 line:80%
because of the Night Orchid.

00:25:34.290 --> 00:25:36.290 line:80%
I wouldn't have needed to use

00:25:36.290 --> 00:25:37.570 line:80%
corpse slaves to lure

00:25:37.570 --> 00:25:39.330 line:80%
Song Xiuzhi and Yang Heying.

00:25:40.220 --> 00:25:41.370 line:80%
Master,

00:25:42.810 --> 00:25:43.980 line:80%
think about Aunt.

00:25:44.370 --> 00:25:46.220 line:80%
You've spent your whole life
avenging her.

00:25:46.740 --> 00:25:47.740 line:80%
Yet you committed

00:25:48.220 --> 00:25:49.890 line:80%
the act of refining corpse slaves.

00:25:51.020 --> 00:25:52.330 line:80%
Can you face her with that?

00:25:52.330 --> 00:25:54.700 line:80%
If I didn't do this,
that'd be betraying Pingshu.

00:25:55.610 --> 00:25:56.980 line:80%
Pingshu is already dead.

00:25:57.460 --> 00:25:58.420 line:80%
These people

00:25:58.700 --> 00:25:59.740 line:80%
don't deserve to live.

00:26:01.090 --> 00:26:02.610 line:80%
If not for you,

00:26:02.610 --> 00:26:04.810 line:80%
Nie Zhe would've long helped me
wipe out the Six Sects.

00:26:04.810 --> 00:26:06.220 line:80%
Then I could kill Nie Zhe in turn

00:26:06.850 --> 00:26:09.460 line:80%
and hand this clean Jianghu

00:26:09.460 --> 00:26:11.050 line:80%
to Zhao and Yuzhi.

00:26:12.890 --> 00:26:14.570 line:80%
Since you love meddling so much,

00:26:14.980 --> 00:26:16.330 line:80%
I'll grant your wish

00:26:16.980 --> 00:26:18.290 line:80%
and send you on your way.

00:26:19.130 --> 00:26:19.970 line:80%
No!

00:26:22.940 --> 00:26:24.290 line:80%
Why do you have no internal power?

00:26:25.303 --> 00:26:27.460 line:80%
Didn't your father pass
all his internal power to you?

00:26:27.460 --> 00:26:29.180 line:80%
I never expected you

00:26:29.180 --> 00:26:31.130 line:80%
to covet my family's things as well.

00:26:31.130 --> 00:26:32.530 line:80%
Unfortunately,

00:26:33.330 --> 00:26:35.130 line:80%
I've given it to someone else.

00:26:35.130 --> 00:26:36.810 line:80%
Useless!

00:26:40.780 --> 00:26:41.620 line:80%
No!

00:27:15.660 --> 00:27:16.570 line:80%
Stop.

00:27:17.330 --> 00:27:18.460 line:80%
Don't keep making mistakes.

00:27:19.500 --> 00:27:20.420 line:80%
I'm not wrong.

00:27:22.180 --> 00:27:23.180 line:80%
I'm not.

00:27:23.610 --> 00:27:24.890 line:80%
I must avenge my master,

00:27:25.850 --> 00:27:26.690 line:80%
my uncle,

00:27:27.850 --> 00:27:29.460 line:80%
and my fellow disciples.

00:27:29.940 --> 00:27:30.880 line:80%
It's been over a decade.

00:27:31.220 --> 00:27:32.060 line:80%
The world

00:27:32.420 --> 00:27:34.290 line:80%
no longer remembers their names.

00:27:37.940 --> 00:27:38.850 line:80%
But I remember.

00:27:48.180 --> 00:27:49.610 line:80%
Ms. Cai was broad-minded.

00:27:52.940 --> 00:27:54.290 line:80%
But I can't do the same.

00:28:12.050 --> 00:28:12.980 line:80%
Wenxun, don't!

00:28:30.700 --> 00:28:31.660 line:80%
Master!

00:28:34.700 --> 00:28:35.540 line:80%
Master!

00:28:37.660 --> 00:28:38.500 line:80%
Master!

00:28:49.700 --> 00:28:50.540 line:80%
Master...

00:28:51.660 --> 00:28:52.610 line:80%
Master...

00:30:35.420 --> 00:30:36.460 line:80%
Master,

00:30:36.460 --> 00:30:37.940 line:80%
you have to kill me first.

00:30:58.050 --> 00:30:58.890 line:80%
Father.

00:30:58.890 --> 00:31:00.700 line:80%
(Pillar of Jianghu)

00:31:03.500 --> 00:31:04.460 line:80%
Let them go.

00:31:05.420 --> 00:31:06.500 line:80%
Otherwise,

00:31:06.500 --> 00:31:08.220 line:80%
you'll never master the Ziwei Method.

00:31:29.610 --> 00:31:31.290 line:80%
The Disintegration.

00:31:36.500 --> 00:31:37.370 line:80%
Master,

00:31:38.500 --> 00:31:39.700 line:80%
stop.

00:32:12.610 --> 00:32:13.500 line:80%
Master,

00:32:14.780 --> 00:32:16.290 line:80%
Aunt once said

00:32:16.940 --> 00:32:18.420 line:80%
that having a conscience

00:32:19.500 --> 00:32:22.050 line:80%
matters more than following rules.

00:32:23.290 --> 00:32:24.330 line:80%
And now,

00:32:25.020 --> 00:32:26.740 line:80%
for the sake of Jianghu rules,

00:32:27.370 --> 00:32:29.130 line:80%
you've thrown away your conscience.

00:32:31.980 --> 00:32:32.820 line:80%
Have you

00:32:35.980 --> 00:32:37.370 line:80%
forgotten all of it?

00:33:06.980 --> 00:33:08.660 line:80%
A skin-painted demon.

00:33:42.530 --> 00:33:44.570 line:80%
You're not a skin-painted demon.

00:34:05.180 --> 00:34:06.020 line:80%
Zhao.

00:34:07.740 --> 00:34:08.930 line:80%
Master.

00:34:11.490 --> 00:34:12.660 line:80%
I'm sorry.

00:34:18.370 --> 00:34:19.850 line:80%
Send me

00:34:23.490 --> 00:34:25.330 line:80%
to see your aunt.

00:35:45.890 --> 00:35:46.730 line:80%
Yunke.

00:35:47.930 --> 00:35:48.770 line:80%
Pingshu.

00:36:47.500 --> 00:36:53.980 line:80%
(Past and Future Glory)

00:36:59.801 --> 00:37:10.461 line:80%
=Generation to Generation=

00:37:29.221 --> 00:37:33.631 line:80%
♪The breeze is gentle,
and spring is fair♪

00:37:34.196 --> 00:37:38.811 line:80%
♪I roam the rivers and hills
in the martial world♪

00:37:39.151 --> 00:37:43.716 line:80%
♪With a shining cup,
I drink with delight tonight♪

00:37:44.241 --> 00:37:48.541 line:80%
♪Free to wander in the world♪

00:37:51.486 --> 00:37:56.186 line:80%
♪I drink with the breeze,
lost in my dreams♪

00:37:56.711 --> 00:38:01.001 line:80%
♪I rest beneath the stars' soft gleam♪

00:38:01.661 --> 00:38:05.691 line:80%
♪The night is calm, still as a stream♪

00:38:06.006 --> 00:38:11.131 line:80%
♪It washes away all judgment and scheme♪

00:38:11.706 --> 00:38:16.516 line:80%
♪I drink with the breeze,
lost in my dreams♪

00:38:16.731 --> 00:38:20.901 line:80%
♪I hold the bright moon
as I return home♪

00:38:21.626 --> 00:38:25.561 line:80%
♪I freely roam in the world♪

00:38:26.061 --> 00:38:31.336 line:80%
♪All I ask is that you go with me♪

00:38:54.066 --> 00:38:59.196 line:80%
♪I drink with the breeze,
lost in my dreams♪

00:38:59.561 --> 00:39:03.931 line:80%
♪I hold the bright moon
as I return home♪

00:39:04.196 --> 00:39:08.326 line:80%
♪I freely roam in the world♪

00:39:08.511 --> 00:39:14.086 line:80%
♪All I ask is that you go with me♪